snippet.title: Epic Tabletop RPG Adventure Awaits! Clash of Clans New Season
snippet.description:
Step into a world of magic, mystery, and epic quests! Our latest season brings the thrill of tabletop RPGs to life. Whether you're a seasoned adventurer or a new hero, this is your chance to prove your mettle. With new challenges, exclusive rewards, and endless adventure, the path to glory starts here!

Learn more about what is to come: https://supercell.com/en/games/clashofclans/blog/news/tabletop-rpg-adventure-awaits/


Follow us on our Socials!

From rage-Â­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

snippet.description:

What is NASA searching for in the deep ocean? Yes, what secrets lie 10 km beneath the ocean's surface that NASA is desperately trying to uncover?

Few people know that just off the coast of Florida, at a depth of 20 meters in the ocean, lies the world's only underwater lab called Aquarius Reef Base. Every year, NASA sends 5-6 researchers and astronautsâ€”yes, astronautsâ€”to this lab for several weeks as part of a special project called Project NEEMO (NASAâ€™s Extreme Environment Mission Operations). These NASA scientists are referred to as "Aquanauts." But that's not all. NASA also has an autonomous underwater vehicle named ORPHEUS, which is diving 10 km deep into the ocean to conduct research. But why is a space agency like NASA working in the depths of the ocean? After all, the U.S. has a separate organization, NOAA (National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration), specifically for ocean research.
What is so urgent that a 2-month deadline has been set? Let's try to understand what's going on in the minds of NASA scientists and whether we should be concerned about it.

In this powerful talk, #Salhabeegum , a #contentcreator  and #sociaworker , shares her courageous story of overcoming life's toughest challenges. Having faced #depression  and loss in her personal life, including the struggles of #motherhood  , #business  setbacks, and the loss of her father, Salha opens up about her darkest moments. But what makes her story truly remarkable is her unwavering determination and resilience. She reveals how she turned her struggles into strengths and found a way to rise above adversity, ultimately achieving success in her career as a student with an #llb  degree. Join us as Salha shares her inspiring journey of transformation, offering valuable lessons on how to overcome obstacles, build resilience, and find purpose in the face of adversity.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam-speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayalis by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayalis. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags-to-riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, womenâ€™s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. In this powerful talk, #Salhabeegum , a #contentcreator  and #sociaworker , shares her courageous story of overcoming life's toughest challenges. Having faced #depression  and loss in her personal life, including the struggles of #motherhood  , #business  setbacks, and the loss of her father, Salha opens up about her darkest moments. But what makes her story truly remarkable is her unwavering determination and resilience. She reveals how she turned her struggles into strengths and found a way to rise above adversity, ultimately achieving success in her career as a student with an #llb  degree. Join us as Salha shares her inspiring journey of transformation, offering valuable lessons on how to overcome obstacles, build resilience, and find purpose in the face of adversity.

Subscribe to Josh Talks Malayalam for more inspiring stories of individuals who have broken free from societal expectations and achieved success in their way.

snippet.description:
Visfot is a gripping crime thriller that explores the dangerous consequences of deceit and poor choices. The film follows the lives of two families, one living in a Mumbai slum and the other in a luxurious high-rise, whoseSS paths intertwine unexpectedly. A series of events leads to a tragic explosion, leaving one man wrongly accused of a crime he didn't commit. As he fights to clear his name, he uncovers a web of corruption and deceit that threatens to destroy everything he holds dear.

We visited her beautiful Dadar home overlooking the sea link and had a heartfelt chat about her memories of Dadar, her love for food, and her journey to Bollywood, including winning the Best Debut Award and her upcoming projects.

snippet.title: Vinayagar Chathurthi Pillayarpatti Modagam Recipe in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video we will see how to make modagam recipe in tamil. This modagam recipe is a large kozhukattai which is made from pacharisi, moong dal, coconut and jaggery. This sweet recipe is popular during the vinayagar chathurthi festival. This sweet recipe is very quick and easy to make and these kolukattai are very tasty.
#modagamrecipe #kozhukkattai #kollukattai 

Friends please do try this modagam kozhukattai recipe at home and share it with your friends and family. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!

Ingredients:
Makes 12 large Kozhukattai:
I have used 125 ml cup to measure all the ingredients
1 cup Raw Rice (100g)ingredients)
1/2 cup Moong dal (50g)
3/4 cup grated coconut
2 cup Jaggery (200g)
1/5 tbsp Ghee
3 cup Water

snippet.title: Venkat Prabhu Interview With Baradwaj Rangan | The GOAT | Conversations | Part 2
snippet.description:

snippet.title: Honey Singh on 'Glory', Mafia Mundeer, Ghostwriting, InternationalÂ VillagerÂ 2 | Podcast | The Quint
snippet.description:
Become The Quint's member now: https://rb.gy/yj715w

In this episode of 'Do I Like It', Prateek Lidhoo talks to one of the most impactful artists of Indian hip hop, Yo Yo Honey Singh. He talks about his comeback as a producer, the writing process of his album 'Glory', and whether he has used ghostwriters in the past. Watch till the end to find out updates about his much anticipated album 'International Villager 2'. 

Chapters:
0:00 - Intro
1:13 - Why is the new album called 'Glory'?
2:50 - What about 'International Villager 2'?
4:27 - How did he find the sound of the album
8:13 - Did Honey Singh use ghostwriters on 'International Villager' and 'Desi Kalakaar'
16:11 - How does Honey Singh feel when people say that he uses ghostwriters?
20:48 - "Mafia Mundeer was never a team"
25:21 - Which was the hardest song to crack?
27:25 - Honey Singh's most underrated song
28:06 - Honey SIngh's least favourite superhit song
29:39 - 10 year plan and 'International Villager 2' update

snippet.description:

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble.
